snippet.title: Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth: Hacker's Memory - Release Date Trailer | PS4, PSV
snippet.description:
Digi-Destined!  By pre-ordering Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth: Hacker's Memory, you'll receive tons of special pre-order bonuses like four bonus Digimon and exclusive costumes! The special Digimon include Omnimon NX, Sistermon Ciel and Blanc, Leopardmon NX, and Crusadermon NX, while costumes include the V. Uchida Costume, Inoden School Attire, and special T shirts! 

Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth: Hacker' Memory will be available on January 19th, 2018, for the PS4 and PSV.
